text: Yuliya Larionova (born 18 August 1984) is an Azerbaijani football referee and a former player who played as a forward. She has been a member of the Azerbaijan women's national team. ==References== Category:1984 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football forwards Category:Women association football referees Category:Women's association football referees Category:Azerbaijani women's footballers Category:Azerbaijan women's international footballers Category:Azerbaijani football referees
